'''Phemiss Bridge''' was the main bridge of access to the city of [[Phemiss]] on [[New Plympto/Legends|New Plympto]]. It crossed the [[Pharine River]].<ref name="CatCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

